<h1>NC News API Documents</h1>
<h2>GET /api</h2>
<p>Brings you to this page!</p>

<h2>GET /api/topics</h2>
<p>Get all the topics</p>

<h2>GET /api/topics/:topic_slug/articles</h2>
<p>
  Return all the articles for a certain topic e.g:
  `/api/topics/football/articles`
</p>

<h2>POST /api/topics/:topic_slug/articles</h2>
<p>
  Add a new article to a topic. This route requires a JSON body with title and
  body key value pairs e.g: `{ "title": "Who dat", "body": "Who dat who dat who
  dat", "created_by": "5bd080de8bbc631964814e2f", "belongs_to": "mitch"}`
</p>

<h2>GET /api/articles</h2>
<p>Returns all the articles</p>

<h2>GET /api/articles/:article_id</h2>
<p>Get an individual article</p>

<h2>DELETE /api/articles/:article_id</h2>
<p>Delete an individual article</p>

<h2>GET /api/articles/:article_id/comments</h2>
<p>Get all the comments for a individual article</p>

<h2>POST /api/articles/:article_id/comments</h2>
<p>
  Add a new comment to an article. This route requires a JSON body with body and
  created_by key value pairs e.g: `{"body": "This is my new comment",
  "created_by": "user_id goes here"}`
</p>

<h2>PATCH /api/articles/:article_id</h2>
<p>
  Increment or Decrement the votes of an article by one. This route requires a
  vote query of 'up' or 'down' e.g: `/api/articles/:article_id?vote=up`
</p>

<h2>PATCH /api/comments/:comment_id</h2>
<p>
  Increment or Decrement the votes of a comment by one. This route requires a
  vote query of 'up' or 'down' e.g: `/api/comments/:comment_id?vote=down`
</p>

<h2>DELETE /api/comments/:comment_id</h2>
<p>Deletes a comment</p>

<h2>GET /api/users/:username</h2>
<p>
  e.g: `/api/users/mitch123` Returns a JSON object with the profile data for the
  specified user.
</p>

<h2>GET /api/users/:userId/articles</h2>
<p>
  e.g: `/api/users/5bd31619f920ba73ca051541` Returns a JSON object with all of
  the articles posted by a specific user
</p>

<h2>GET /api/users/:userId/comments</h2>
<p>
  e.g: `/api/users/5bd31619f920ba73ca051541` Returns a JSON object with all of
  the comments posted by a specific user
</p>
